name: Fuki
description:
A commission of @Wiggyfreak1.

Fuki (aka Fuki Commune) is a Japanese singer, the vocalist of DOLL$BOXX and Unlucky Morpheus.

1500-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images (kindly provided by @Wiggyfreak1) with my usual settings.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
